2%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20said%20Thursday%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bserious%20questions%26quot%3B%20about%20Washington's%20plan%20for%20a%2030-day%20ceasefire%20in%20Ukraine%20but%20Moscow%20was%20ready%20to%20discuss%20it%20with%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20made%20his%20first%20comments%20on%20the%20plan%2C%20which%20Ukraine%20agreed%20to%20Tuesday%20at%20talks%20with%20the%20United%20States%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bfor%26quot%3B%20the%20proposed%20ceasefire%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20nuances%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bserious%20questions%26quot%3B%20about%20how%20it%20would%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20told%20reporters%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20need%20to%20talk%20to%20our%20American%20colleagues...%20Maybe%20have%20a%20phone%20call%20with%20President%20Trump%20and%20discuss%20this%20with%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20called%20for%20Russia%20to%20agree%20a%20ceasefire%20without%20any%20conditions%2C%20with%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20saying%20Tuesday%3A%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20we%20want%20to%20know%20--%20if%20they're%20prepared%20to%20do%20it%20unconditionally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20Putin's%20statement%20was%20%26quot%3Bpromising%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3Bnot%20complete%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20details%20of%20a%20final%20agreement%20have%20actually%20been%20discussed.%20Now%20we're%20going%20to%20see%20if%20Russia%20is%20there%20and%2C%20if%20not%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20very%20disappointing%20moment%20for%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20love%20to%20meet%20with%20him%20or%20talk%20to%20him.%20But%20we%20have%20to%20get%20it%20over%20with%20fast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20earlier%20said%20at%20his%20press%20conference%20that%20Russia%20would%20take%20its%20%26quot%3Bnext%20steps%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20as%20its%20forces%20make%20rapid%20progress%20on%20the%20front%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20visiting%20a%20military%20headquarters%20in%20the%20Kursk%20region%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Russian%20president%20hailed%20troops'%20progress%20against%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Russian%20troops%20were%20%26quot%3Badvancing%20in%20practically%20all%20areas%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20front%20line%20and%20%26quot%3Bbased%20on%20how%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20develops%2C%20we%20will%20agree%20on%20the%20next%20steps%20in%20ending%20the%20conflict%20and%20reaching%20agreements%20acceptable%20to%20all%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Trump%20pushes%20for%20a%20speedy%20end%20to%20the%20more%20than%20three-year%20conflict%2C%20his%20envoy%20Steve%20Witkoff%20arrived%20in%20Moscow%20Thursday%20to%20discuss%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20top%20Kremlin%20aide%2C%20Yuri%20Ushakov%2C%20said%20Witkoff%20would%20meet%20Putin%20on%20Thursday%20evening%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bclosed%20format%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20comments%20to%20Izvestia%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20been%20grinding%20forward%20on%20the%20battlefield%20for%20over%20a%20year%2C%20and%20claimed%20on%20Thursday%20to%20have%20driven%20Ukrainian%20forces%20from%20the%20town%20of%20Sudzha%20in%20Russia's%20Kursk%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20expressed%20optimism%20that%20his%20team%20can%20secure%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20despite%20Moscow's%20battlefield%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20get%20Russia%20to%20stop%2C%20then%20we%20have%20a%20full%20ceasefire.%20And%20I%20think%20it'll%20never%20go%20back%20to%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20reporters%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20earlier%20Thursday%20had%20criticised%20the%20lack%20of%20an%20official%20response%20from%20Moscow%2C%20saying%20on%20social%20media%20that%20this%20shows%20%26quot%3BRussia%20seeks%20to%20prolong%20the%20war%20and%20postpone%20peace%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Long-term%20peace'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20talks%2C%20Putin%20said%20Thursday%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20agree%20with%20proposals%20to%20cease%20hostilities%2C%20but%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20cessation%20would%20lead%20to%20long-term%20peace%20and%20address%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20the%20crisis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20already%20ruled%20out%20accepting%20foreign%20peacekeepers%20in%20Ukraine%20as%20part%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20or%20long-term%20security%20guarantee%20for%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20go%20against%20a%20request%20Ukraine%20has%20made%20of%20European%20allies%20to%20deploy%20military%20%26quot%3Bcontingents%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20territory%20once%20the%20conflict%20ends%20to%20protect%20against%20future%20attacks%20from%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20absolutely%20unacceptable%20to%20us%20that%20army%20units%20of%20other%20states%20be%20stationed%20in%20Ukraine%20under%20any%20flag%2C%26quot%3B%20Russian%20foreign%20ministry%20spokeswoman%20Maria%20Zakharova%20said%20in%20a%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBe%20it%20a%20foreign%20contingent%20or%20a%20military%20base...%20all%20this%20would%20mean%20the%20involvement%20of%20these%20countries%20in%20a%20direct%20armed%20conflict%20with%20our%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattle%20for%20Kursk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20claimed%20rapid%20advances%20in%20the%20Kursk%20region%20--%20where%20Kyiv%20launched%20a%20cross-border%20assault%20last%20August%20and%20has%20held%20territory%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20defence%20ministry%20said%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bliberated%26quot%3B%20Sudzha%20along%20with%20two%20other%20settlements%20in%20the%20border%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudzha%2C%20home%20to%20around%205%2C000%20people%20before%20the%20fighting%2C%20was%20the%20largest%20settlement%20Kyiv%20seized%20after%20it%20launched%20its%20shock%20assault%20into%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kursk%20region%20was%20one%20of%20Kyiv's%20few%20bargaining%20chips%20in%20swapping%20land%20with%20Russia%2C%20which%20has%20occupied%20around%20a%20fifth%20of%20Ukraine%20since%20it%20took%20Crimea%20in%202014%20and%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20assault%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine%20now%20risks%20losing%20its%20grip%20on%20the%20border%20region%20entirely%2C%20ceding%20dozens%20of%20square%20kilometres%20(miles)%20in%20the%20past%20seven%20days%2C%20according%20to%20military%20bloggers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20commander-in-chief%20Oleksandr%20Syrsky%20hinted%20late%20Wednesday%20that%20some%20of%20its%20troops%20were%20pulling%20back%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20Sumy%20region's%20military%20administration%20said%20on%20Facebook%20on%20Thursday%20it%20had%20ordered%20the%20mandatory%20evacuation%20of%20eight%20villages%20near%20the%20border%20with%20Kursk%2C%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bthe%20exacerbation%20of%20the%20operational%20situation%20in%20the%20region%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bconstant%20shelling%20by%20Russia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20visited%20Kursk%20on%20Wednesday%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20Ukraine%20launched%20its%20incursion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDressed%20in%20battle%20fatigues%2C%20he%20expressed%20hope%20his%20army%20would%20%26quot%3Bfully%20liberate%26quot%3B%20areas%20under%20Kyiv's%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow's%20rapid%20advances%20in%20the%20region%20came%20after%20the%20US%20paused%20intelligence-sharing%20and%20security%20support%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20although%20analysts%20and%20officials%20cautioned%20against%20making%20a%20direct%20link.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20said%20it%20had%20resumed%20its%20support%20for%20Kyiv%20ahead%20of%20the%20talks%20wi