e%20federal%20workforce%2C%20led%20by%20the%20White%20House's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-agencies-musk-doge-targeted-list-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%20%3C%2Fa%3Eoffice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlsup%20previously%20ruled%20the%20OPM%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20have%20any%20authority%20whatsoever%2C%20under%20any%20statute%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20universe%26quot%3B%20to%20tell%20another%20agency%20to%20fire%20its%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20new%20ruling%20orders%20the%20departments%20of%20Defense%2C%20Treasury%2C%20Energy%2C%20Interior%2C%20Agriculture%2C%20and%20Veterans%20Affairs%20to%20offer%20fired%20probationary%20employees%20their%20jobs%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20IRS%20employee%20who%20was%20terminated%20in%20February%2C%20and%20who%20expects%20to%20be%20reinstated%20following%20Alsup's%20order%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20pretty%20awesome.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20relieving%20to%20an%20extent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20job-hunting%20and%20had%20an%20interview%20yesterday%2C%20but%20obviously%20you%20never%20know%20when%20you'll%20get%20a%20job%20offer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20IRS%20employee%20was%20more%20wary%2C%20anxious%20that%20Trump%20would%20just%20pursue%20another%20way%20to%20fire%20him%20and%20believing%20a%20private%20sector%20job%20could%20offer%20more%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EEven%20without%20an%20offer%2C%20my%20initial%20reaction%20is%20extreme%20stress%2C%20concern%2C%20and%20worry%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20get%20the%20offer%20and%20take%20the%20job%20back%2C%20will%20this%20happen%20again%3F%20What%20I%20used%20to%20think%20was%20a%20job%20with%20great%20job%20security%20is%20now%20not%20so%20secure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverett%20Kelley%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20American%20Federation%20of%20Government%20Empl