20claimed%20the%20government%20was%20punishing%20it%20for%20its%20reportage%20that%20focussed%20on%20its%20shortcomings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Congress%20spokesperson%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20government%20had%20reduced%20spending%20on%20newspaper%20advertisements%20and%20that%20it%20was%20a%20prerogative%20of%20the%20government%20who%20they%20want%20to%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20newspaper%20has%20exposed%20incidents%20of%20communal%20unrest%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20since%20the%20Congress%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20highlighting%20police%20failures%20and%20the%20state's%20inaction.%20It%20has%20reported%20on%20the%20demolition%20of%20an%20abandoned%20mosque%20in%20Chilkur%2C%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20dupatta%20from%20minority%20schoolgirls'%20uniforms%2C%20and%20the%20government's%20failure%20to%20protect%20Waqf%20properties.%20Munsif%20has%20also%20raised%20delayed%20salaries%20of%20imams%20and%20muezzins%2C%20non-payment%20of%20stipends%20for%20divorced%20women%2C%20and%20the%20Congress's%20failure%20to%20include%20a%20Muslim%20representative%20in%20the%20Telangana%20cabinet-just%20as%20it%20had%20criticized%20the%20Modi%20government%20for%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20statement%20by%20Ather%20Moin%2C%20the%20newspaper's%20Executive%20Editor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Revanth%20government%20expects%20us%20to%20convince%20our%20readers%20that%20Telangana%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20land%20of%20milk%20and%20honey%20under%20Congress%20rule%2C%20then%20that%20is%20something%20we%20cannot%20do.%20Instead%2C%20we%20shall%20continue%20to%20ask%3A%20Why%20have%20lands%20turned%20barren%3F%20Why%20has%20starvation%20forced%20the%20poor%20to%20the%20brink%3F%20Why%20have%20helpless%20daughters%20been%20violated%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20has%20also%20targetted%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20pointing%20to%20his%20statement%20in%20Washington%20in%20June%20202