ts%20and%20death%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOGE%20staffers%20are%20from%20a%20hodgepodge%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-agencies-musk-doge-targeted-list-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20agencies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20at%20least%20four%20are%20engineers.%20As%20part%20of%20their%20duties%2C%20they've%20been%20given%20access%20to%20Americans'%20personal%2C%20non-anonymized%20data%2C%20the%20agency's%20chief%20information%20officer%20and%20a%20human%20resources%20executive%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20the%20employees%2C%20whose%20names%20weren't%20released%2C%20received%20privacy%20and%20ethics%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20assignments%20are%20the%20latest%20twist%20in%20the%20White%20House's%20crusade%20against%20death-related%20skullduggery.%20The%20administration%20has%20suggested%20that%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-security-elon-musk-doge-fraud-trump-retirement-dead-americans-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etens%20of%20millions%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20of%20dead%20people%20are%20claiming%20Social%20Security%20benefits%2C%20but%20the%20agency's%20inspector%20general%20has%20conducted%20audits%20that%20suggest%20it's%20a%20much%20smaller%20problem%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202021%20audit%20found%20that%20the%20SSA%20paid%20out%20%24298%20million%20to%2024%2C000%20dead%20Americans%20through%20December%202019.%20And%20while%20billions%20of%20dollars%20are%20paid%20out%20in%20error%20more%20broadly%20every%20year%2C%20it's%20a%20drop%20in%20the%20bucket%20compared%20to%20the%20over%20%241%20trillion%20in%20annual%20benefits%20the%20agency%20pays%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeland%20Dudek%2C%20the%20acting%20head%20of%20the%20SSA%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssa.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress%2Freleases%2F2025%2F%232025-03-05%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esought%20to%20clarify%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20information%20flagged%20by%20Musk%20and%20the%20White%20House%20isn't%20evidence%20of%20fraud%2C%20even%20as%20he%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssa.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress%2Freleases%2F2025%2F%232025-02-19%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefended%3C%2Fa%3E%20DOGE's%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Frecording-reveals-leland-dudek-thoughts-trump-doge-social-security%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProPublica%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Dudek%20talked%20candidly%20about%20DOGE%20during%20a%20recorded%20meeting%20with%20senior%20staff%20members%20and%20Social%20Security%20advocates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20person%20at%20the%20meeting%20asked%20why%20he%20hadn't%20pushed%20back%20more%20on%20Trump's%20false%20claims%20of%20fraud%2C%20and%20Dudek%20seemed%20to%20suggest%20there%20was%20only%20so%20much%20he%20could%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we%20published%2C%20for%20the%20record%2C%20what%20was%20actually%20the%20numbers%20there%20on%20our%20website.%20This%20is%20dealing%20with%20%E2%80%94%20have%20you%20ever%20worked%20with%20someone%20who's%20manic-depressive%3F%26quot%3B%20Dudek%20said%20on%20a%20recording%2C%20ProPublica%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetirement%20policy%20experts%20have%20sounded%20the%20alarm%20for%20decades%20about%20Social%20Security's%20inability%20to%20provide%20benefits%20once%20its%20funds%20run%20out%2C%20which%20the%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssa.gov%2Fpolicy%2Ftrust-funds-summary.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimated%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20happen%20in%202035.%20The%20SSA%20and%20outside%20experts%20have%20proposed%20raising%20taxes%20or%20reducing%20benefit%20payments%20to%20stave%20that%20off%2C%20but%20Congress%20hasn't%20acted%20on%20the%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaste%2C%20fraud%2C%20and%20abuse%20have%20been%20deeply%20entrenched%20in%20our%20broken%20system%20for%20far%20too%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Harrison%20Fields%2C%20a%20White%20House%20deputy%20press%20secretary%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20direct%20access%20to%20the%20system%20to%20identify%20and%20fix%20it.%20DOGE%20will%20continue%20to%20shine%20a%20light%20on%20the%20fraud%20they%20uncover%20as%20the%20American%20people%20deserve%20to%20know%20what%20their%20government%20has%20been%20spending%20their%20hard%20earned%20tax%20dollars%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Social%20Security%20Administration%20press%20office%20and%20Katie%20Miller%2C%20an%20advisor%20to%20DOGE%2C%20didn't%20reply%20to%20emails%20seeking%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavits%20filed%20Wednesday%20also%20said%20that%20two%20DOGE%20employees%2C%20one%20detailed%20from%20NASA%20and%20the%20other%20from%20the%20General%20Services%20Administration%2C%20have%20access%20to%20data%20on%20the%20SSA's%20workforce%20or%20are%20advising%20on%20things%20like%20%26quot%3Binefficiencies%20and%20areas%20for%20improvement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Prospect%20and%20the%20Associated%20Press%20have%20reported%20that%20up%20to%2050%25%20of%20the%20agency's%20staff%20could%20be%20cut%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssa.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress%2Freleases%2F2025%2F%232025-02-28%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20agency%20has%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20those%20claims%20are%20false%20and%20it's%20only%20targeting%20a%2012.3%25%20reduction%20in%20head%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20agencies%20have%20been%20ordered%20to%20submit%20workforce-downsizing%20plans%20to%20the%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20by%20March%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%2099%25%20of%20the%20money%20allocated%20to%20the%20Social%20Security%20Administration%20each%20year%20is%20paid%20to%20beneficiaries%2C%20with%20just%200.5%25%20of%20spending%20amounting%20to%20%26quot%3Badministrative%20expenses%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssa.gov%2Foact%2FSTATS%2Fadmin.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20agency's%20website%20says%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-dead-people-social-security-administration-benefits-fraud-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741887425000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672e5adb88cea3ba1c1f46bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-dead-people-social-security-administration-benefits-fraud-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20assignments%20are%20the%20latest%20twist%20in%20the%20White%20House's%20crusade%20against%20death-related%20skullduggery.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jnewsham%40insider.com%20(Jack%20Newsham)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A275%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-dead-people-social-security-administration-benefits-fraud-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Promotes%20Secessionist%20Sentiments%26quot%3B%3A%20N%20Sitharaman%20Slams%20DMK's%20Rupee%20Move%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20was%20the%20last%20to%20weigh%20in%20today%20on%20the%20DMK's%20move%20to%20replace%20the%20rupee%20symbol%20with%20the%20Tamil%20letter%20(Ru)%2C%20but%20with%20the%20sharpest%20barb.%20The%20move%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bsignals%20a%20dangerous%20mindset%20that%20weakens%20Indian%20unity%20and%20promotes%20secessionist%20sentiments%20under%20the%20pretence%20of%20regional%20pride%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20avoidable%20example%20of%20language%20and%20regional%20chauvinism%26quot%3B.%20She%20also%20questioned%20why%20the%20DMK%20had%20not%20made%20its%20reservations%20known%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20ruling%20DMK%20had%20replaced%20the%20Devnagari%20rupee%20symbol%20(Re)%20in%20promotional%20material%20for%20the%20state%20budget%20-%20due%20on%20Friday%20morning%20--%20making%20a%20point%20amid%20the%20blazing%20row%20over%20what%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3Bimposition%20of%20Hindi%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Centre%20through%20its%20mandatory%20three-language%20policy%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResult%20--%20since%20morning%2C%20the%20party%20has%20drawn%20massive%20political%20backlash.%20%C2%A0State%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Annamalai%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20rupee%20symbol%20accepted%20by%20the%20nation%20has%20been%20drawn%20dram%20by%20the%20son%20of%20a%20former%20DMK%20MLA%2C%20tagged%20the%20state's%20ruling%20party%20%26quot%3Bstupid%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Governor%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Tamilisai%20Soundarajan%2C%20alleged%20the%20swap%20%26quot%3Bis%20against%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B%20and%20challenged%20Mr%20Stalin%20to%20change%20his%20name%20to%20a%20Tamil%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20evening%2C%20the%20finance%20minister%20put%20in%20her%20response%20with%20a%20lengthy%20post%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20DMK%20of%20%26quot%3Butterly%20disregarding%20the%20creative%20contribution%20of%20a%20Tamil%20youth%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20elected%20representatives%20and%20authorities%20are%20sworn%20under%20the%20Constitution%20to%20uphold%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20our%20nation.%20Removing%20a%20national%20symbol%20like%20'Rs'%20from%20the%20State%20Budget%20documents%20goes%20against%20that%20very%20oath%2C%20weakening%20the%20commitment%20to%20national%20unity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20government%20has%20reportedly%20removed%20the%20official%20Rupee%20symbol%20'Rs'%20from%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Budget%202025-26%20documents%2C%20which%20will%20be%20presented%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20DMK%20government%20has%20reportedly%20removed%20the%20official%20Rupee%20symbol%20'%E2%82%B9'%20from%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Budget%202025-26%20documents%2C%20which%20will%20be%20presented%20tomorrow.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIf%20the%20DMK%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farivalayam%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40arivalayam%3C%2Fa%3E)%20has%20a%20problem%20with%20'%E2%82%B9'%2C%20why%20didn't%20it%20protest%20back%20in%202010%20when%20it%20was%20officially%20adopted%20under%20the...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20(%40nsitharaman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnsitharaman%2Fstatus%2F1900216600823029796%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2013%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Rupee%20symbol%20'%E2%82%B9'%20is%20internationally%20well-recognized%20and%20serves%20as%20a%20visible%20identity%20of%20India%20in%20global%20financial%20transactions.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20India%20is%20pushing%20for%20cross-border%20payments%20using%20UPI%2C%20should%20we%20really%20be%20undermining%20our%20own%20national%20currency%20symbol%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20DMK%20has%20a%20problem%20with%20'%E2%82%B9'%2C%20why%20didn't%20it%20protest%20back%20in%202010%20when%20it%20was%20officially%20adopted%20under%20the%20%40INCIndia-led%20UPA%20government%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20DMK%20was%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20at%20the%20Centre%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20also%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20use%20of%20'Ru'%20only%20is%20meant%20to%20prioritise%20Tamil%20and%20express%20their%20love%20of%20language.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20illegal%20about%20it...%20this%20is%20not%20a%20'showdown'.%20We%20prioritise%20Tamil%2C%20that%20is%20why%20the%20government%20went%20ahead%20with%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20DMK%20leader%20Saravanan%20Annadurai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20election%20year%2C%20the%20DMK%20has%20op