Fmichelle-obamas-podcast-with-brother-craig-robinson-labelled-flop-and-boring-by-fox-news-over-low-viewership%2Farticleshow%2F118987530.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118987530.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fmichelle-obamas-podcast-with-brother-craig-robinson-labelled-flop-and-boring-by-fox-news-over-low-viewership%2Farticleshow%2F118987530.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fmichelle-obamas-podcast-with-brother-craig-robinson-labelled-flop-and-boring-by-fox-news-over-low-viewership%2Famp_articleshow%2F118987530.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fmichelle-obamas-podcast-with-brother-craig-robinson-labelled-flop-and-boring-by-fox-news-over-low-viewership%2Famp_articleshow%2F118987530.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20City%20Is%20The%20World's%20Most%20Polluted.%20Hint%3A%20It's%20Not%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20small%20city%20on%20the%20Meghalaya-Assam%20border%2C%20nearly%202%2C000%20kilometres%20away%20from%20Delhi%2C%20is%20the%20most%20polluted%20in%20the%20world%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20published%20by%20a%20global%20pollution%20watchdog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwiss%20air%20technology%20company%20IQAir's%202024%20World%20Air%20Quality%20Report%2C%20which%20was%20released%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20has%20said%20that%20residents%20of%20Byrnihat%20in%20Meghalaya%20breathe%20the%20most%20toxic%20air%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20small%20industrial%20hub%20that%20is%20home%20to%20several%20factories%2C%20including%20distilleries%2C%20iron%20and%20steel%20plants%2C%20Byrnihat%20recorded%20an%20annual%20average%20PM2.5%20concentration%20of%20128.2%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre%2C%20as%20against%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization's%20(WHO)%20limit%20of%205%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre.%20Byrnihat%20connects%20Shillong%20in%20Meghalaya%20to%20Guwahati%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM2.5%20refers%20to%20tiny%20particulate%20pollutants%20smaller%20than%202.5%20microns%2C%20which%20can%20enter%20the%20lungs%20and%20bloodstream%2C%20leading%20to%20breathing%20problems%2C%20heart%20disease%20and%20even%20cancer.%20The%20sources%20include%20vehicle%20exhausts%2C%20industrial%20emissions%20and%20the%20burning%20of%20wood%20or%20crop%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Byrnihat%20is%20followed%20by%20Delhi%2C%20Karaganda%20(Kazakhstan)%2C%20Lahore%20(Pakistan)%20and%20Faridabad%20(Haryana%2C%20India)%20as%20the%20most%20polluted%20cities%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20air%20quality%20has%20worsened%20and%20it%20remains%20the%20most%20polluted%20capital%20city%20globally%2C%20the%20report%20showed%2C%20with%20the%20annual%20average%20PM2.5%20concentration%20rising%20from%20102.4%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre%20in%202023%20to%20108.3%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20ranked%20as%20the%20world's%20fifth%20most%20polluted%20nation%20last%20year%2C%20marking%20an%20improvement%20from%20its%20third%20rank%20in%202023%2C%20but%2013%20of%20the%20world's%2020%20most%20polluted%20cities%20were%20from%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Byrnihat%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Faridabad%2C%20Punjab's%20Mullanpur%2C%20Loni%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20Ganganagar%2C%20Greater%20Noida%2C%20Bhiwadi%2C%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20Hanumangarh%20and%20Noida%20are%20on%20the%20list.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%2035%25%20of%20the%20Indian%20cities%20reported%20annual%20PM2.5%20levels%20exceeding%2010%20times%20the%20WHO%20limit%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20India%20saw%20a%207%25%20decline%20in%20PM2.5%20concentrations%20in%202024%2C%20averaging%2050.6%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre%2C%20compared%20to%2054.4%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Major%20Sources%20Likely%20On%20Assam%20Side'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20note%20of%20the%20report%2C%20Meghalaya%20Chief%20Minister%20Conrad%20Sangma%20on%20Thursday%20told%20the%20state%20assembly%20that%20the%20Meghalaya%20State%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(MSPCB)%20has%20found%20Byrnihat's%20air%20quality%20to%20be%20satisfactory%2C%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bpoor%20to%20very%20poor%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20recorded%20by%20a%20monitoring%20station%20installed%20in%20the%20Central%20Academy%20for%20State%20Forest%20Service%2C%20across%20the%20border%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20indicates%20that%20the%20major%20sources%20of%20air%20pollution%20may%20be%20attributed%20to%20industrial%20and%20other%20activities%20on%20the%20Assam%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sangma%20said%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20areas%20in%20Byrnihat%20close%20to%20Assam%20have%2020%20%26quot%3Bred%20category%26quot%3B%20(high%20pollution%20potential)%20industries%20while%20the%20Meghalaya%20part%20has%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Mr%20Sangma%20said%20he%20has%20written%20to%20his%20Assam%20counterpart%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20is%20awaiting%20a%20response.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister.%20I%20have%20not%20received%20any%20feedback%20(yet)%20but%20I%20will%20speak%20to%20him%20on%20the%20phone.%20It%20(report)%20is%20of%20great%20concern%20to%20all%20of%20us.%20I%20am%20very%20concerned%20and%20I%20am%20not%20very%20happy.%20I%20will%20definitely%20take%20personal%20interest%20in%20this.%20This%20is%20not%20something%20that%20I%20wa