0at%20the%20mall%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%20night%20was%20a%20big%20deal%20for%20my%20young%20teens.%20These%20get-togethers%20were%20dependent%20on%20parent%20drop-offs%20and%20pickups%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20without%20cellphones%2C%20we%20counted%20on%20everyone%20paying%20attention%20to%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20mass%20school%20shooting%20wouldn't%20happen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-columbine-changed-american-schools-forever-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euntil%20Columbine%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201999.%20My%20teens'%20school%20building%20was%20unlocked%20all%20day%2C%20and%20I%20could%20run%20over%20to%20deliver%20a%20forgotten%20lunch%20or%20sports%20bag%20without%20elaborate%20front%20office%20check-ins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20kids%20could%20still%20look%20forward%20to%20attending%20college%20without%20crushing%20debt%20and%20being%20able%20to%20afford%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22355169e9-8a4f-449e-bdc2-757c86013f06%5C%22%3ELife%20is%20different%20for%20my%20grandkids%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20world%20my%20grandkids%20are%20navigating%20in%20the%20mid-2020s%20as%20they%20enter%20their%20teen%20years%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20far%20different%20world%20than%20the%20one%20of%20their%20parents'%20adolescence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20can't%20imagine%20air%20travel%20or%20attending%20a%20concert%20or%20other%20public%20event%20without%20going%20through%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20there%20were%2083%20school%20shootings%2C%20and%20most%20school%20districts%20began%20active%20shooter%20drills%20in%20elementary%20schools.%20Even%20little%20ones%20know%20where%20to%20hide.%20Today's%20teens%20have%20lived%20through%20COVID%2C%20which%20affected%20every%20facet%20of%20their%20lives.%20My%20older%20grandsons%20were%20out%20of%20school%20for%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half.%20Their%20return%20to%20in-class%20education%20was%20a%20real%20challenge%2C%20and%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20pandemic%20will%20linger%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandkids%20have%20no%20memory%20of%20telephone%20landlines.%20While%20they%20are%20hoping%20to%20get%20flip%20phones%20in%20middle%20school%2C%20many%20of%20their%20friends%20already%20own%20smartphones.%20This%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20arrange%20rides%20home%20but%20also%20to%20be%20victims%20of%20cyberbullying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20costs%20of%20education%20and%20housing%20have%20skyrocketed%20in%20recent%20years.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feducationdata.org%2Faverage-cost-of-college-by-year%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20College%20tuition%20has%20increased%20141%25%20in%20the%20past%2020%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20housing%20costs%20have%20largely%20outpaced%20young%20adults'%20future%20job%20earnings%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fbusiness%2F3478213-rising-home-prices-a-timeline%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSince%25202000%252C%2520median%2520home%2520prices%2Cover%2520the%2520last%2520two%2520decades.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20(161%25%20increase%20in%20home%20prices%20since%202005%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1d27bca-f3cc-42b8-81eb-e2f95235c1c4%5C%22%3EHere's%20my%20advice%20for%20raising%20teens%2C%20even%20in%20today's%20age%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20the%20lines%20of%20communication%20open.%20My%20teens%20stopped%20spontaneously%20sharing%20their%20days%2C%20and%20I%20see%20that%20also%20starting%20to%20happen%20with%20my%20grandsons.%20There's%20a%20lot%20I%20don't%20understand%2C%20and%20admitting%20that%20to%20the%20kids%20is%20a%20good%20thing.%20They%20can%20be%20our%20guides%3B%20they're%20more%20likely%20to%20explain%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20their%20world%20if%20they%20know%20they%20won't%20be%20shut%20down%20with%20criticism.%20And%20when%20they%20get%20those%20phones%2C%20texting%20will%20likely%20become%20the%20main%20way%20they%20interact%20with%20us%20%E2%80%94%20as%20it%20is%20with%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%2