20plan%20is%20being%20prepared%20to%20counter%20it%2C%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20said%20today.%20Mr%20Reddy%2C%20who%20received%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20invitation%20to%20participate%20in%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20on%20the%20matter%20on%20March%2022%2C%20also%20said%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20have%20much%20representation%20from%20the%20southern%20states%20and%20%26quot%3Bwants%20to%20take%20revenge%20on%20these%20states%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20thwart%20the%20conspiracies%20hatched%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Central%20government%20against%20the%20southern%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20underscoring%20that%20he%20is%20extending%20full%20support%20to%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20is%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20delimitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20invitation%20for%20the%20March%2022%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20there%20are%20provisions%20that%20indicate%20that%20the%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%20should%20not%20be%20carried%20out%20until%20the%20national%20census%20is%20conducted%20after%202026.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20central%20government%20has%20%26quot%3Bbrought%20this%20process%20to%20the%20fore%20before%20the%20census%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Ministers%20from%20Kerala%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Punjab%20have%20already%20been%20invited%20to%20join%20the%20Joint%20Action%20Committee%20(JAC)%20to%20deal%20with%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20has%20been%20spearheading%20the%20opposition%20to%20delimitation%20--%20the%20exercise%20to%20redraw%20constituencies%20on%20basis%20of%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20southern%20state%20contends%20that%20against%20the%20untrammelled%20population%20of%20northern%20states%20that%20would%20increase%20their%20seats%20in%20parliament%2C%20its%20success%20with%20family%20planning%20would%20only%20penalise%20it%20with%20a%20reduced%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Chief%20Minister%20Stalin%20and%20his%20son%20and%20Deputy%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20have%20asked%20newlyweds%20to%20have%20children%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20win%20200-plus%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%202026%20elections.%20I%20request%20the%20couples%20who%20are%20getting%20married%20to%20be%20concerned%20about%20childbirth%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Our%20state%20implemented%20birth%20control%20first%2C%20and%20due%20to%20this%2C%20we%20are%20now%20facing%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%20yesterday%20after%20presiding%20over%20a%20mass%20wedding%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%2C%20the%20state%20with%2039%20seats%20might%20lose%20up%20to%20eight%20seats%20in%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20while%20northern%20states%20that%20failed%20to%20check%20population%20would%20get%20around%20100%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Union%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20addressed%20the%20issue%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20not%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20southern%20states%20even%20by%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20reassure%20the%20people%20of%20South%20India%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20kept%20your%20interest%20in%20mind%20and%20will%20make%20sure%20that%20not%20even%20one%20seat%20is%20reduced.%20And%20whatever%20increase%20is%20there%2C%20southern%20states%20will%20get%20a%20fair%20share%2C%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20doubt%20this...%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20after%20delimitation%2C%20on%20pro%20rata%20basis%2C%20not%20a%20single%20seat%20will%20be%20reduced%20in%20any%20southern%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741883100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fljvis7dg_revanth-reddy_625x300_15_Februar