d%2C%20armed%2C%20and%20fully%20equipped%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20entered%20and%20stood%20at%20his%20side%2C%20which%20resulted%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20human%20law%20enforcement%20wall%2C%26quot%3B%20Dickey's%20filing%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20did%20not%20tell%20Mangione%20he%20was%20free%20to%20leave%20and%20gave%20a%20false%20reason%20for%20being%20there%2C%20saying%20he%20%26quot%3Blooked%20suspicious%26quot%3B%20and%20had%20%26quot%3Bover-stayed%20his%20welcome%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20told%20to%20show%20his%20ID%20and%20stand%20with%20his%20hands%20on%20his%20head%2C%20the%20filing%20says.%20He%20was%20then%20frisked%2C%20%26quot%3Balthough%20no%20circumstances%20existed%20at%20that%20time%20justifying%20said%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20plenty%20of%20probable%20cause%20to%20detain%20and%20question%20Mangione%20at%20this%20point%2C%20legal%20experts%20told%20BI.%20Mangione's%20face%20had%20been%20online%20and%20on%20TV%20for%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20like%20a%20rock%20star%20%E2%80%94%20everyone%20knows%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Scotto%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20somebody%20spots%20the%20guy%20at%20McDonald's%2C%20then%20the%20police%20are%20obviously%20going%20to%20come%20in%20and%20take%20defensive%20positions%20around%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20are%20also%20within%20their%20rights%20to%20ask%20what%20are%20called%20%26quot%3Binvestigatory%26quot%3B%20questions%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20your%20name%3F%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%20are%20you%20from%3F%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20in%20the%20backpack%3F%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20before%20Mirandizing%20a%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pennsylvania%20defense%20filing%20describes%20a%20series%20of%20what%20are%20all%20permissible%20police%20actions%2C%20legal%20experts%20said%20%E2%80%94%20including%20any%20lies%20told%20about%20his%20overstaying%20his%20welcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20obligated%20to%20explain%20anything%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Al-Shabazz%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20allowed%20to%20lie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20officers%2C%20the%20suppression%20motion%20says%2C%20continued%20to%20%26quot%3Binterrogate%20and%20question%26quot%3B%20Mangione%2C%20asking%20whether%20a%20nearby%20backpack%2C%20plastic%20bag%2C%20and%20other%20items%20were%20his.%20One%20officer%2C%20the%20motion%20adds%2C%20left%20briefly%20to%20run%20his%20New%20Jersey%20ID%2C%20which%20police%20would%20later%20say%20was%20fake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%2017%20minutes%20passed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20officers%20were%20present%20%E2%80%94%20by%20the%20time%20Mangione%20was%20read%20his%20Miranda%20rights.%20He%20shook%20his%20head%20no%20when%20asked%20whether%20he%20wished%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20defense%20filing%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20more%20questioning%20and%20another%20pat-down%2C%20the%20document%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3Bhe%20was%20then%20placed%20in%20handcuffs%20and%20was%20informed%20that%20he%20was%20being%20detained%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bphysically%20removed%20from%20the%20McDonald's.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20probable%20cause%20for%20this%20arrest%2C%20legal%20experts%20said%3A%20the%20Jersey%20ID%20that%20police%20said%20is%20fake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276203bd5-6402-40ce-869b-ff7e87483877%5C%22%3ENo%20guns%20were%20drawn%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20who%20stayed%20behind%20then%20took%20a%20look%20through%20his%20belongings%20%E2%80%94%20what%20the%20filing%20alleges%20was%20an%20illegal%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20search%20of%20the%20backpack%2C%20the%20Altoona%20Police%20uncovered%20a%20clip%20wrapped%20up%20in%20underwear%20and%20other%20items%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20says%2C%20referring%20to%20evidence%20later%20inventoried%20as%20a%20magazine%20holding%2012%20rounds%2C%20including%20three%20hollow-point%20rounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20computer%20chip%20was%20found%20wrapped%20in%20duct%20tape%2C%20which%20one%20officer%20removed%20using%20a%20knife%2C%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20a%20valid%20search%20warrant%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione's%20bags%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20department%2C%20where%20a%20search%20of%20the%20backpack%20revealed%20the%20gun%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bmanifesto%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20everything%20else%20on%20the%20inventory%2C%20the%20filing%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20searched%20it%20as%20part%20of%20the%20arrest%20process%2C%20as%20part%20of%20securing%20his%20property%20%E2%80%94%20they%20don't%20need%20a%20warrant%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Scotto%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20wasn't%20just%20picking%20him%20up%20for%20jaywalking.%20What%20if%20he%20had%20a%20bomb%20in%20that%20bag%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20prosecutor%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20know%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20it's%20not%20like%20they%20came%20at%20him%20with%20guns%20drawn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224826%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luigi%20Mangione%2C%20suspect%20in%20the%20fatal%20shooting%20of%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson%2C%20is%20escorted%20into%20a%20Manhattan%20courtroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d0c522b8b41a9673fa5949%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223217%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMangione%20is%20fighting%20to%20suppress%20the%20gun%2C%20writings%2C%20and%20electronics%20seized%20from%20him%20during%20his%20arrest%20at%20a%20McDonald's.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Hirsch%2FNew%20York%20Post%20via%20AP%2C%20Pool%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDickey%20is%20also%20seeking%20to%20suppress%20everything%20Mangione%20told%20the%20police.%20A%20judge%20may%20disallow%20anything%20Mangione%20said%20in%20response%20to%20police%20questioning%20after%20he%20was%20Mirandi