he%20month%20leading%20up%20to%20and%20following%20the%20accident%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2025%2F03%2F11%2Flifestyle%2Fonlyfans-model-mercedes-valentine-suffers-memory-loss-after-crash%2F%5C%22%3E%20New%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20open%20my%20eyes%2C%20I%20sometimes%20don't%20even%20recognize%20myself.%20Because%20I%20function%20differently%20and%20can't%20remember%20most%20things%2C%20it's%20like%20my%20brain%20is%20someone%20else's.%20It's%20been%20really%20confusing%20and%20emotionally%20challenging%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with.%20I've%20had%20to%20start%20living%2C%20and%20adapting%20to%20doing%20so%2C%20as%20a%20different%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fneedtoknow.co.uk%2F%5C%22%3ENeedToKnow.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20fateful%20summer%20of%202024%2C%20Ms%20Valentine's%20had%20a%20thriving%20career.%20She%20had%20just%20purchased%20a%20lavish%20house%20for%20over%20%24900%2C000%20and%20a%20sleek%20blue%20Porsche%20Taycan%20Turbo%20for%20over%20%24100%2C000.%20A%20day%20before%20the%20accident%2C%20she%20was%20celebrating%20her%20parents'%2060th%20birthdays%20and%20retirement.%20When%20it%20was%20time%20to%20leave%2C%20she%20opted%20to%20ride%20her%20motorcycle%20home%20instead%20of%20joining%20her%20family%20in%20their%20car%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20forever%20altered%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20being%20clever%20and%20was%20going%20very%20fast%20down%20a%20residential%20street%20where%20there%20was%20a%20pigeon%20on%20the%20lamppost%20above%20me.%20As%20I%20approached%2C%20it%20swooped%20down%20and%20not%20knowing%20what%20it%20was%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20avoid%20it.%20But%20then%20it%20hit%20me%20head%20and%20I%20swerved%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENY%20Post.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20swerved%20to%20avoid%20the%20bird%2C%20her%20motorcycle%20crashed%20into%20a%20parked%20car%2C%20sending%20her%20flying%20260%20feet%20through%20the%20air.%20She%20landed%20six%20houses%20away%20from%20the%20point%20of%20impact%2C%20following%20which%20bystanders%20rushed%20to%20call%20for%20emergency%20assistance.%20Fortunately%2C%20Valentine's%20family%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20are%20medical%20professionals%2C%20were%20driving%20behind%20her%20and%20were%20able%20to%20provide%20immediate%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20lying%20in%20the%20road%20for%20about%20two%20minutes%20before%20they%20arrived.%20I%20was%20blue%20and%20not%20responding%2C%20my%20pupils%20were%20dilated%20and%20it%20was%20assumed%20I%20was%20dead.%20My%20dad%20ultimately%20saved%20my%20life%2C%20as%20he%20took%20off%20my%20helmet%20to%20stop%20it%20from%20choking%20me%20and%20stop%20the%20bleeding%20as%20best%20he%20could%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20then%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20it%20was%20discovered%20that%20she%20lost%20over%20three%20litres%20of%20blood%20from%20the%20incident.%20As%20per%20doctors%2C%20Ms%20Valentine%20faced%20the%20possibility%20of%20blindness%2C%20double%20vision%2C%20and%20total%20limb%20numbness%20once%20her%20physical%20wounds%20healed.%20Additionally%2C%20she%20suffered%20from%20Ehlers-Danlos%20syndrome%2C%20a%20condition%20that%20weakens%20joints%20and%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Valentine%20finally%20regained%20consciousness%20a%20week%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20she%20could%20only%20recall%20her%20boyfriend's%20name%2C%20Mark%2C%20and%20her%20family%20members.%20Everything%20else%2C%20including%20the%20accident%20itself%2C%20was%20a%20complete%20blank.%C2%A0After%20a%20month-long%20hospital%20stay%2C%20she%20was%20finally%20discharged%20and%20returned%20home%2C%20eager%20to%20resume%20her%20life.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20only%20then%20that%20the%20full%20extent%20of%20her%20memory%20loss%20became%20clear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20shocking%20and%20traumatizing.%20I'd%20be%20at%20the%20gym%2C%20and%20someone%20would%20say%20hello%20and%20I'd%20have%20no%20clue%20who%20they%20were.%20I%20quickly%20had%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20my%20memory%20was%20never%20coming%20back.%20Time%20is%20completely%20warped%20to%20me%20now.%20I%20forget%20what%20day%20or%20month%20it%20is%20regularly.%20My%20boyfriend%20has%20to%20give%20me%20a%20run%20every%20day%20of%20what%20I've%20got%20on%2C%20otherwise%2C%20I'd%20forget%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20shared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20attempts%20to%20revive%20her%20content%20creation%2C%20she's%20faced%20with%20insensitive%20comments%20about%20her%20appearance%2C%20specifically%20her%20bruised%20eye%20and%20scars.%20Despite%20the%20challenges%2C%20Valentine%20has%20taken%20responsibility%20for%20the%20accident%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20greater%20caution%20could%20have%20prevented%20it.%20She's%20using%20her%20experience%20to%20caution%20fellow%20bike%20riders%2C%20stressing%20the%20importance%20of%20situational%20awareness%2C%20knowing%20one's%20limits%2C%20and%20always%20wearing%20a%20helmet%C2%A0because%20it%20ultimately%20saved%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741870920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fckcoruao_mercedes-valentine_625x300_13_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fneuroscientist-turned-onlyfans-model-suffers-memory-loss-after-brutal-bike-accident-7916694%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20crash%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20Valentine's%20mental%20health%2C%20causing%20memory%20loss%20that%20erased%20her%20recollections%20of%20the%20month%20leading%20up%20to%20and%20following%20the%20accident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fneuroscientist-turned-onlyfans-model-suffers-memory-loss-after-bruta